\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZDAK.html#IMMZDAK-Theclientisseverelyimmunocompromised-60\">The client is severely immunocompromised-60</a></td><td>The client is severely immunocompromised</td><td><div><p>\"Potential contraindications\" = \"Severely immunocompromised\"</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"IMMZD5DTHepatitisAContraindicationsVS-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK-The|20client|20has|20a|20history|20of|20severe|20allergic|20reactions-60\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZDAK.html#IMMZDAK-Theclienthasahistoryofsevereallergicreactions-60\">The client has a history of severe allergic reactions-60</a></td><td>The client has a history of severe allergic reactions</td><td><div><p>'\"Potential contraindications\" = \"Severe allergic reactions\"</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"IMMZD5DTHepatitisAContraindicationsVS-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK-Hepatitis|20A|20vaccination|20could|20be|20contraindicated.|20Clinical|20judgement|20is|20required.|20Create|20a|20clinical|20note-66\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZDAK.html#IMMZDAK-HepatitisAvaccinationcouldbecontraindicated.46Clinicaljudgementisrequired.46Createaclinicalnote-66\">Hepatitis A vaccination could be contraindicated. Clinical judgement is required. Create a clinical note-66</a></td><td>Hepatitis A vaccination could be contraindicated. Clinical judgement is required. Create a clinical note</td><td><div><p>\"Immunization recommendation status\" = \"Further evaluation needed\"</p>\n</div></td></tr></table></div>"
